>\n喂阿哥，佢係咁關心個囡而唔選，佢直情而家就宣布辭職啦。</blockquote><br />\n世事都俾你睇穿晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1ff8f627eceb59e0679d3ef283f4433d559c5a","tid":31061,"uid":62127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892863955d0fdf4a25821632fa26b6fbd8012fcf","tid":31061,"uid":11706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我等睇689話：我個囡依家好番，可以將心機擺番係政策入面，所以宣布出來競選連任。<br />\n喂阿哥，佢係咁關心個囡而唔選，佢直情而家就宣布辭職啦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見個個都唔報名，就黎招以退為進，<br />\n引蛇出洞，再爆黑材料，然後宣布因無人能勝任，本人迎難而上，盡力無私奉獻香港多五年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4834599853a6b221e2e1d5b44a2bf7340c2af760","tid":31061,"uid":56807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:38:00.000Z","msg":"一陣又係語言偽術我就笑，成個記招689只話唔參選無話唔連任，只要爆醜聞令到其他人退選/唔選，佢就可以唔參選但自動連任。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d998ae6b533f1e096c6292e3589255d13535c9","tid":31061,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:41:51.000Z","msg":"盲毛燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac586cbee821a097ce380e3e524920c16272bf9","tid":31061,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「林鄭唔選特首梁振英入閘機會高」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos